Big Brother Naija, BBNaija, housemate, Kiddwaya on Friday disclosed that his relationship with fellow housemate, Erica would continue after the reality television show. Kiddwaya made the disclosure during a conversation with Brighto. Brighto had asked what would happen to Kiddwaya’s relationship with Erica at the end of the reality television show. Responding, the 27-year-old said: “Yes of course definitely will.” Kiddwaya is currently in a love triangle with Erica and Laycon. A few days ago, Kiddwaya had said he would support Erica if she opted for Laycon ahead of him The 27-year-old had also described Erica as just his friend.